race.description: Ladbrokes Big Bets Copy Now Class 3 Plate
race.comment: ZOUBABY (13) was beaten under a length in consecutive races over 1000m then tackled a 1200m Class 6 at the Gold Coast last start and was out of her depth. Finds a far more suitable race today so a return to form looks likely. The lightly raced and promising YOYO YEEZY (8) opened this prep with a couple of wins then went around at $1.80 last time but was edged out over 1000m at the Sunshine Coast. His only run at this trip was his worst but it was on debut so worth forgiving. On-pacer who is sure to give a great sight. NEIL (5) went to the paddock off a good win at Randwick and while this is another step, he is only lightly raced and trending the right way. AIR WE GO (1) is another up in grade, but hard to knock winning form and has to be included.
